{"tid":1645600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國咁封殺落去，會唔會有一日封到無野好封","createTime":"2019-10-11T02:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T03:03:50.000Z","uid":228995,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"33b27a1c17d318d273271eedf78fac344d6859a1","tid":1645600,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"邊際效用遞減法則，中學econ 101。<br />\n<br />\n中國封殺遊戲、電影、音樂界別。<br />\n第一個被封殺對象可能會驚，經濟影響可能好大。<br />\n但當被封殺嘅人愈來愈多，被封殺對象可能會慢慢無感覺。<br />\n被封殺對象甚至可能自己組成一個消費群體。<br />\n就好似香港黃色經濟圈一樣。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，中國ban第一個人個效益可能好大，但當ban到第100個、1000個時，作用就會愈來愈細。"},{"pid":"3f49510aabbe608f2383282d31e3381fac25dbad","tid":1645600,"uid":14262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"北韓後塵"},{"pid":"6853fb4b74d5a54dadbf5217984fa4ea3cf56518","tid":1645600,"uid":286238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"agreed!!"},{"pid":"521f025feaa5544f9768555d36b8914abbf60bbc","tid":1645600,"uid":105578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}